<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div id="contentInfo" class="large-6 columns">
      <h4>In the last 20 years, Haiti has experienced over 20 major natural disasters.</h4> <br>
      <%= line_chart @countries.group(:year).count, height: '300px', colors: ["#2E4159"], library: {
        title: {text: 'Disaster Timeline', x: -20},
        yAxis: {
           allowDecimals: false,
           title: {
               text: 'Occurences'
           }
        },
        xAxis: {
           title: {
               text: 'Year'
           }
        }
      }  %>

      Flooding, hurricanes, cholera, and earthquakes have impeded communities' continual efforts to return to normalcy.<br>

      <%= bar_chart @countries.group(:disaster).count, height: '300px', colors: ["#2E4159"], library: {
        title: {text: 'Disaster Types by Occurence', x: -20},
        yAxis: {
           allowDecimals: false,
           title: {
               text: 'Occurences'
           }
        },
        xAxis: {
           title: {
               text: 'Disaster Types'
           }
        }
      } %>

      There were 10,257 civilian casualties over that 20 year time span, not including the 2010 earthquake. The Haitian government reported the death toll to have surpassed 230,000 people after the second quake passed.

      <%= pie_chart @countries.group(:disaster).sum(:total_affected), height: '300px', library: {
        title: {text: 'Total Affected by Disasters', x: -20},
      } %>

      <%= pie_chart @countries.group(:disaster).sum(:deaths), height: '300px', library: {
        title: {text: 'Deaths by Disasters', x: -20} }%>

      <%= pie_chart @countries.group(:disaster).sum(:affected), height: '300px', library: {
        title: {text: 'Affected by Disasters', x: -20} }%>

      <%= pie_chart @countries.group(:disaster).sum(:injured), height: '300px', library: {
        title: {text: 'Injured by Disasters', x: -20} }%>

      <%= pie_chart @countries.group(:disaster).sum(:homeless), height: '300px', library: {
        title: {text: 'Displaced by Disasters', x: -20} }%>

      <br>
      <br>
      Most international non-profits create a rallying cry around natural disasters to bootstrap donations, <br>
      but over time 3rd party analysis, along with investigative journalism, determined that many international non-profits were incredibly ineffective <br>
      in bringing meaningful changes to communities that were not understood by the employees who lacked the shared lived experience.
      <br>
      <br>
      <h3> ... So how can my resources reach the impacted communities? </h3>






